8 An Act relating to motor vehicle safety; amending 47
O.S. 2021, Section 11-902, which relates to persons
9 under the influence of alcohol or other intoxicating
substance; modifying sentencing provisions for
10 certain violations; modifying scope of certain
offense; modifying scope of penalties for certain
11 offense; updating statutory language and references;
and providing an effective date.
